- xs: 0.75rem

**CSS Variables:**
```css
--font-display: 'Playfair Display', serif;
--font-heading: 'Syne', sans-serif;
--font-body: 'Inter', sans-serif;
```

### Spacing System

Based on 4px base unit:
- `--space-1`: 4px
